tempo-myprofile: Label of one of two menus in the top navigation, providing links to a user's pages (such as talk page, contributions, user page, and preferences)
tempo-notifications: Label of the second of two menus in the top navigation to be used for implementation of the Echo extension and new talk notifications
tempo-nonotifications: When there are no notifications to show in the menu, this message is shown.
tempo-hello: A generic greeting shown in the top navigation near the menus
tempo-guest: The name used to refer to users who are not logged in (in the hello message)
